Major change: removed sufficiently confident classifiers, simplified and improved the rest

 The calculations with sufficiently confident fake classifiers resulted in less
 impressive results than originally anticipated. The class of models for which analytical
 calculations could be performed did not contain realistic classifiers.
 Therefore, with a heavy heart I remove them from the codebase. May they rest in git history
